<body>
<header class="top"><div class="brand"><h1>Opportunity Room Power Calculator</h1><p>Mixed branch circuits, cabinet-level add circuits, panel inventory, amp validation, and OP-factor checks</p></div><button class="btn" onclick="toggleTheme()" id="themeBtn">Dark mode</button><button class="btn" onclick="saveProject()">Save JSON</button><label class="btn" for="loadFile">Load JSON</label><input id="loadFile" class="hidden" type="file" accept="application/json" onchange="loadProject(event)"><button class="btn green" onclick="exportExcel()">Export Excel</button><button class="btn primary" onclick="window.print()">PDF / Print</button></header>
<div id="criticalModal" class="modalback" onclick="if(event.target.id==='criticalModal')closeCriticalModal()"><div class="modal"><h2 id="criticalModalTitle">🚨 Critical Engineering Error</h2><div id="criticalModalCopy"></div><ul id="criticalModalList"></ul><div class="actions"><button class="btn primary" onclick="closeCriticalModal()">I'll fix it before Erick opens Outlook</button><button class="btn" onclick="closeCriticalModal();showView('summary',document.querySelector('.tab[onclick*=summary]'))">Show validation</button></div></div></div>
<div class="wrap">
<aside class="panel left">
<section class="sec"><div class="title"><span class="dot"></span>Project</div><div class="grid2"><div class="field"><div class="lbl">Customer</div><input id="customer" value="Customer Name" oninput="calc()"></div><div class="field"><div class="lbl">Opportunity</div><input id="oppty" value="OPP-0000" oninput="calc()"></div><div class="field"><div class="lbl">Site</div><input id="site" value="Site / DC" oninput="calc()"></div><div class="field"><div class="lbl">Engineer</div><input id="engineer" value="Alex" oninput="calc()"></div><div class="field"><div class="lbl">Date</div><input id="date" type="date" oninput="calc()"></div><div class="field"><div class="lbl">CIM / Quote</div><input id="ticket" value="CIM-0000" oninput="calc()"></div></div><div class="field"><div class="lbl">Notes</div><textarea id="notes" oninput="calc()">Draft provisioning design for sales engineering review.</textarea></div></section>
<section class="sec"><div class="title"><span class="dot"></span>Base Opportunity Questions</div><div class="grid2"><div class="field"><div class="lbl">Licensed Power kW</div><input id="licensedPower" type="number" min="0" step=".1" value="100" oninput="calc()"></div><div class="field"><div class="lbl">Allowable OP Factor</div><input id="opFactor" type="number" min="0" step=".01" value="1.25" oninput="calc()"></div></div><div class="info" id="licenseInfo"></div></section>
<section class="sec"><div class="title"><span class="dot"></span>Distribution</div><div class="grid2"><div class="field"><div class="lbl">Distribution Type</div><select id="distribution" onchange="syncDistribution();calc()"><option value="single">Single source</option><option value="2n" selected>2N panel pair</option><option value="4to3">4-to-3 / 3-of-4</option></select></div><div class="field"><div class="lbl">Source Set</div><select id="sourceSet" onchange="calc()"></select></div><div class="field"><div class="lbl">Default Map Panel Type</div><select id="panelType" onchange="calc()"></select></div><div class="field"><div class="lbl">Assignment</div><select id="method" onchange="calc()"><option value="balanced">Balanced round-robin</option><option value="sequential">Sequential fill</option><option value="bestfit">Best fit by kW</option></select></div></div><details style="margin-top:8px"><summary style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);cursor:pointer;font-weight:700">Advanced</summary><div class="field" style="margin-top:10px"><div class="lbl">Start Pole / First Available Breaker Position</div><input id="startPole" type="number" min="1" value="1" oninput="calc()"><p class="hint">Leave at 1 for empty panels. Change only if the first breaker positions are already reserved or used.</p></div></details><div class="info" id="catalogInfo"></div></section>
<section class="sec"><div class="title"><span class="dot"></span>Panel Inventory</div><div class="info" style="margin-bottom:10px">Select the panel types available for this design and set quantities. Validation checks requested continuous amps against this inventory.</div><div id="panelInvBody" class="invCards"></div><div class="actions"><button class="btn" onclick="addPanelInventoryRow()">+ Add Panel Type</button></div></section>
<section class="sec"><div class="title"><span class="dot"></span>Controls</div><button class="btn primary" style="width:100%" onclick="generateWithCriticalCheck()">Generate / Refresh</button><div class="actions"><button class="btn" onclick="addRequest()">+ Cabinet</button><button class="btn red" onclick="clearRequirements()">Clear requirements</button></div><p class="hint">Each power requirement can use a different branch circuit type. 2N can use any source pair, including B+D. 4-to-3 provisions each request across three selected sources.</p></section>
</aside>
<main class="panel right">
<nav class="tabs"><button class="tab active" onclick="showView('library',this)">Cabinet Library</button><button class="tab" onclick="showView('input',this)">Power Requirements</button><button class="tab" onclick="showView('summary',this)">Summary</button><button class="tab" onclick="showView('maps',this)">Panel Maps</button><button class="tab" onclick="showView('output',this)">Report</button></nav>
<section id="view-library" class="view active"><div class="info" style="margin-bottom:14px"><b>Cabinet Library</b><br>Use <b>Row / Zone Ranges</b> when rows have different cabinet counts. Example: Row 1 start 101 with Qty 10 generates 101-110; Row 2 can use 0201-0222. Generating cabinets replaces the existing library and creates matching Power Requirement rows.</div><h3>Row / Zone Ranges</h3><div class="tablewrap" style="margin-bottom:10px"><table><thead><tr><th>Row</th><th>Zone / RPP Area</th><th>Start Cabinet</th><th>End Cabinet</th><th>Qty</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody id="rowRangeBody"></tbody></table></div><div class="actions"><button class="btn" onclick="addRowRange()">+ Add row range</button><button class="btn primary" onclick="generateCabinetLibrary()">Generate Cabinets</button><button class="btn" onclick="addLibraryCabinet()">+ Add Cabinet</button><button class="btn" onclick="addBulkCabinetsFromText()">+ Bulk Cabinets</button><button class="btn red" onclick="resetCabinetLibrary()">Reset to 100-199</button></div><div class="tablewrap"><table><thead><tr><th>Row</th><th>Zone</th><th>Cabinet Number</th><th>Used</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody id="cabLibBody"></tbody></table></div></section>
<section id="view-input" class="view"><div class="info" style="margin-bottom:12px"><b>Bulk apply to all cabinet rows</b><br>Use this when most cabinets use the same power design. You can edit individual rows afterward.</div><div class="grid3"><div class="field"><div class="lbl">Branch Circuit</div><select id="bulkBranch" onchange="syncBulkKwFromBranch(true)"></select></div><div class="field"><div class="lbl">Circuit Qty</div><input id="bulkCircuits" type="number" min="0" value="2"></div><div class="field"><div class="lbl">Expected kW Each</div><input id="bulkKwEach" type="number" min="0" step=".01" value="17.25"><p class="hint">Defaults to the selected circuit continuous kW (80%). Override only when needed.</p></div></div><div class="actions"><button class="btn primary" onclick="applyBulkRequirements()">Apply to All Cabinets</button><button class="btn" onclick="addRequest()">+ Cabinet</button><button class="btn" onclick="duplicateLast()">Duplicate last requirement</button><button class="btn" onclick="importCsvPrompt()">Import CSV text</button></div><div class="tablewrap"><table><thead><tr><th>Row</th><th>Zone</th><th>Cabinet</th><th>Branch Circuit</th><th>Circuit Qty</th><th>Expected kW Each</th><th>Source Override</th><th>PDU / Requirement</th><th>Notes</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody id="reqBody"></tbody></table></div></section>
<section id="view-summary" class="view"><div class="kpis" id="kpis"></div><div class="info" id="requiredInfo" style="margin-bottom:14px"></div><div class="actions"><button class="btn primary" onclick="showView('summary',document.querySelector('.tab[onclick*=summary]'));renderEngineeringReview()">🔍 Engineering Review</button></div><div id="engineeringReview" class="reviewBox"></div><div class="validation" id="validation"></div><h3>Panel Utilization</h3><div class="cards" id="utilCards"></div><div id="utilNote"></div><h3>Phase Balance</h3><div class="phasebox" id="phaseCards"></div><div id="phaseNote" class="info"></div></section>
<section id="view-assign" class="view"><div class="tablewrap"><table><thead><tr><th>Cabinet</th><th>Request</th><th>Branch</th><th>Expected kW</th><th>Source Placements</th><th>Phases</th><th>Status</th></tr></thead><tbody id="assignBody"></tbody></table></div></section>
<section id="view-maps" class="view"><div id="mapsBySource"></div></section>
<section id="view-output" class="view"><div id="printOut"></div></section>
</main>
</div>
